Resource Profile: CH ELM Patient

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-elm/StructureDefinition/ch-elm-patient Version: 1.0.0-trialuse
Draft as of 2023-09-13 Computable Name: ChElmPatient

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This CH ELM base profile constrains the Patient resource for the purpose of laboratory orders and test reports.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CH ELM Document: Laboratory Report
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH ELM Composition: Laboratory Report, CH ELM DiagnosticReport: Laboratory Report, CH ELM Observation Results: Laboratory, CH ELM ServiceRequest: Laboratory Order and CH ELM Specimen: Laboratory
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Patient/1Pat-DM, Patient/Pat-E5, Patient/Pat-ET, Patient/Pat-ErnstKarlTanner and Patient/Pat-LillyLiechtenstein
